{"word":"H5526 - סָכַךְ - çâkak - saw-kak' - Cover","slug":"H5526","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">סָכַךְ</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>çâkak"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>saw-kak'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Cover"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E9;&#x05C2;&#x05DB;&#x05DA;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#x05E1;&#x05DB;&#x05DA; - sa&#x0302;kak  s&#x0301;a&#x0302;kak</b> - <i>saw-kak', saw-kak'</i><p/>A primitive root; properly to <i>entwine</i> as a screen; by implication to <i>fence</i> in, <i>cover</i> over, (figuratively) <i>protect: - </i>cover, defence, defend, hedge in, join together, set, shut up."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H7900\">H7900</a>"}]}